  "description": "Implements crafting recipes for non-craftable vanilla items, with a focus on fitting with the game's progression and reducing the grinding aspect of the game.",
  "body": "# Uncraftables\n\n<a href='https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api'>\n  <img alt='fabric-api' height='40' src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact/requires/fabric-api_vector.svg'>\n</a>\n\n## About\n\nImplements crafting recipes for non-craftable vanilla items, with a focus on fitting with the game's progression and reducing the grinding aspect of the game.\n\n## Installation\n\nAdd the `.jar` file to your `.minecraft\\mods` directory, along with [Fabric Loader](https://fabricmc.net/use/installer/) and [Fabric API](https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api).\n\n## Recipes\n\nThe latest version implements the following recipes:\n\n| Item                 | Recipe                                                                                         |\n| ---                  | ---                                                                                            |\n| Amethyst Shard       | <img alt='amethyst-shard-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/wkolcn.png'>       |\n| Bell                 | <img alt='bell-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/2fxuho.png'>                 |\n| Brown Mushroom       | <img alt='brown-mushroom-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/6s3qkm.png'>       |\n| Brown Mushroom Block | <img alt='brown-mushroom-block-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/m0s3nc.png'> |\n| Cobweb               | <img alt='cobweb-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/wljxwq.png'>               |\n| Dead Bush            | <img alt='dead-bush-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/u8vx0o.png'>            |\n| Diamond Horse Armor  | <img alt='diamond-horse-armor-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/t9q7m4.png'>  |\n| Elytra               | <img alt='elytra-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/i8y1lo.png'>               |\n| Golden Horse Armor   | <img alt='golden-horse-armor-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/o9ld1r.png'>   |\n| Ice                  | <img alt='ice-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/bb83og.png'>                  |\n| Iron Horse Armor     | <img alt='iron-horse-armor-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/e1j08c.png'>     |\n| Name Tag             | <img alt='name-tag-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/12njik.png'>             |\n| Nether Wart          | <img alt='nether-wart-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/i0oeae.png'>          |\n| Packed Ice           | <img alt='nether-wart-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/d15jfk.png'>          |\n| Red Mushroom         | <img alt='red-mushroom-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/67576k.png'>         |\n| Red Mushroom Block   | <img alt='red-mushroom-block-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/nf61aw.png'>   |\n| Saddle               | <img alt='saddle-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/zo8wah.png'>               |\n| Totem of Undying     | <img alt='totem-of-undying-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/s0n9jd.png'>     |\n| Trident              | <img alt='trident-recipe' height='200' src='https://files.catbox.moe/szi6n7.png'>              |\n\n## License\n\nThis mod is licensed under the MIT License. Feel free to learn from it and incorporate it in your own projects.\n",
